('Healthcare Document Processing', 
E'A large healthcare network was processing thousands of patient records, insurance claims, and medical documents daily. Manual data entry was slow, error-prone, and consuming significant staff resources.\n\nWe implemented an AI-powered document processing system that:\n\n• Automatically extracts data from medical records, insurance forms, and referrals\n• Validates information against existing patient databases\n• Flags inconsistencies and potential errors for review\n• Routes documents to appropriate departments automatically\n• Ensures HIPAA compliance throughout the process\n• Integrates with existing EMR systems\n\nTechnology Stack:\n• Computer vision for document scanning and OCR\n• Natural language processing for medical terminology\n• Machine learning for data validation\n• Secure, encrypted data handling\n• Audit trails for compliance\n\nOutcomes:\n• 90% reduction in manual data entry time\n• 75% decrease in processing errors\n• 100% HIPAA compliance maintained\n• $500K annual cost savings\n• Staff redeployed to patient care activities\n• Average processing time reduced from 48 hours to 4 hours',
'https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1576091160399-112ba8d25d1d?w=1080&q=80',
'["https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1584982751601-97dcc096659c?w=1080&q=80", "https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1504813184591-01572f98c85f?w=1080&q=80", "https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1585421514738-01798e348b17?w=1080&q=80"]'::jsonb,
null,
