('Financial Fraud Detection System',
E'A fintech startup needed to protect their rapidly growing user base from fraudulent transactions while minimizing false positives that would frustrate legitimate customers.\n\nWe developed a real-time fraud detection system powered by machine learning that:\n\n• Analyzes transaction patterns in real-time\n• Identifies anomalies and suspicious behavior\n• Adapts to new fraud techniques automatically\n• Provides risk scores for each transaction\n• Minimizes false positives through intelligent scoring\n• Integrates with existing payment infrastructure\n\nKey Capabilities:\n• Real-time transaction analysis (< 100ms response time)\n• Behavioral biometrics and device fingerprinting\n• Network analysis to identify fraud rings\n• Continuous learning from confirmed fraud cases\n• Customizable risk thresholds per transaction type\n• Detailed audit logs and reporting\n\nBusiness Results:\n• 95% fraud detection rate\n• 60% reduction in false positives\n• $2M+ in prevented fraudulent transactions annually\n• Processing time under 100ms for seamless UX\n• Enabled expansion into higher-risk markets\n• Regulatory compliance maintained',
'https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1563986768609-322da13575f3?w=1080&q=80',
'["https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1551288049-bebda4e38f71?w=1080&q=80", "https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1460925895917-afdab827c52f?w=1080&q=80", "https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1454165804606-c3d57bc86b40?w=1080&q=80", "https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1590283603385-17ffb3a7f29f?w=1080&q=80"]'::jsonb,
null,
