('Supply Chain Optimization Platform',
E'A manufacturing company with complex global supply chains was facing frequent delays, inventory issues, and inefficient resource allocation. Traditional planning methods couldn''t handle the complexity.\n\nWe built an AI-powered supply chain optimization platform that:\n\n• Predicts demand patterns across multiple product lines\n• Optimizes inventory levels at each warehouse location\n• Identifies potential supply chain disruptions before they occur\n• Recommends optimal shipping routes and methods\n• Automates reordering based on predictive analytics\n• Provides real-time visibility across the entire supply chain\n\nAdvanced Features:\n• Multi-variable demand forecasting\n• Weather and events impact analysis\n• Supplier reliability scoring\n• Dynamic route optimization\n• Inventory optimization algorithms\n• What-if scenario modeling\n• Integration with ERP, WMS, and TMS systems\n\nMeasurable Impact:\n• 30% reduction in inventory carrying costs\n• 45% decrease in stockout incidents\n• 25% improvement in on-time delivery rates\n• $1.5M annual savings in transportation costs\n• 40% faster response to supply chain disruptions\n• Improved supplier relationship management',
'https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1586528116311-ad8dd3c8310d?w=1080&q=80',
'["https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1494412574643-ff11b0a5c1c3?w=1080&q=80", "https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1553413077-190dd305871c?w=1080&q=80", "https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1578575437130-527eed3abbec?w=1080&q=80"]'::jsonb,
null,
false,
