('Recruitment AI Screening Tool',
E'A fast-growing tech company was receiving 10,000+ applications monthly for various roles. Their HR team of 8 people was overwhelmed, and qualified candidates were slipping through the cracks or waiting weeks for responses.\n\nWe developed an AI-powered recruitment screening system that:\n\n• Analyzes resumes and applications automatically\n• Matches candidates to job requirements intelligently\n• Eliminates unconscious bias in initial screening\n• Conducts preliminary interviews via chat\n• Schedules qualified candidates for human interviews\n• Provides detailed candidate insights to recruiters\n\nEthical AI Features:\n• Bias detection and mitigation algorithms\n• Transparent scoring methodology\n• Compliance with employment regulations\n• Candidate privacy protection\n• Human oversight at critical decision points\n• Continuous auditing for fairness\n\nRecruitment Outcomes:\n• 95% reduction in initial screening time\n• 70% increase in qualified candidate identification\n• Time-to-hire reduced from 45 to 18 days\n• 40% improvement in candidate diversity\n• Enhanced candidate experience with faster responses\n• HR team refocused on strategic talent initiatives\n• 85% recruiter satisfaction with AI recommendations',
'https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1521737711867-e3b97375f902?w=1080&q=80',
'["https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1573496359142-b8d87734a5a2?w=1080&q=80", "https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1554224155-6726b3ff858f?w=1080&q=80", "https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1512314889357-e157c22f938d?w=1080&q=80", "https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1542744173-8e7e53415bb0?w=1080&q=80"]'::jsonb,
